# Keep the deployment to the site itself.
#
# .superpowers/ is the SDD ledger — internal build notes, gitignored and not
# public on GitHub. Listed explicitly rather than relying on Vercel's
# .gitignore fallback, because publishing it would put those notes on a public
# URL. tools/ and docs/ are dev-side only (the checker, the generator, specs
# and plans); they are public on GitHub already, they just have no reason to
# be served.
.superpowers/
tools/
docs/
.DS_Store
